[Cite as 10/2812002 Case Announcements, 2002-Ohio-5854.]

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

October 28, 2002

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2001- 1158. Cincinnati SMSA L.P. v. Pub. Util. Comm.

Public Utilities Commission, No. 93-1758-RC-CSS. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Public Utilities Commission of Ohio. Upon consideration of the motion for admission pro hac vice by Mark I. Walleh for Seamus C. Duffy,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for admission pro hac vice be, and hereby is, granted.

Cook, J., dissents.
